---
---
<section id="servicios" class="section servicios">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="servicios__header reveal">
      <p class="section-tag">Lo que ofrecemos</p>
      <h2>Nuestros <span class="text-green">servicios</span></h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Main cards A B C -->
    <div class="cards-main reveal-group">
      <!-- A: Perros -->
      <div class="svc-card">
        <div class="svc-card__img">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/perros/600/400" alt="Hospedaje perros" loading="lazy" />
          <span class="svc-card__badge">🐕 Perros</span>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-card__body">
          <h3>Hospedaje para perros</h3>
          <p>Perros en libertad en grupos homogéneos, siempre supervisados. Descanso cómodo y seguro por la noche.</p>
          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5491150968576&text=Hola!%20Quiero%20informaci%C3%B3n%20de%20hospedaje%20para%20mi%20perro." target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary svc-card__cta">Consultar</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- B: Gatos -->
      <div class="svc-card">
        <div class="svc-card__img">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/gatos1/600/400" alt="Hospedaje gatos" loading="lazy" />
          <span class="svc-card__badge">🐈 Gatos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-card__body">
          <h3>Hospedaje para gatos</h3>
          <p>Gateras amplias e individuales, ambientadas con troncos, plantas y casitas para que se sientan en casa.</p>
          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5491150968576&text=Hola!%20Quiero%20informaci%C3%B3n%20de%20hospedaje%20para%20mi%20gato." target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary svc-card__cta">Consultar</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- C: Traslados locales -->
      <div class="svc-card">
        <div class="svc-card__img">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/traslado/600/400" alt="Traslados" loading="lazy" />
          <span class="svc-card__badge">🚐 Traslados</span>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-card__body">
          <h3>Traslados a domicilio</h3>
          <p>Retiro y devolución con camionetas acondicionadas y personal capacitado.</p>
          <div class="hours">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            <span>Lunes a viernes: 8:00 a 16:00 hs</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5491150968576&text=Hola!%20Quiero%20informaci%C3%B3n%20sobre%20traslados." target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary svc-card__cta">Consultar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card D: Adiestramiento (wider) -->
    <div class="card-adiest reveal" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
      <div class="card-adiest__media">
        <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1PuD3h2bmSUsGT3GxdfnZfLG7OH6izvJp" alt="Adiestramiento" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://picsum.photos/seed/adiest/600/500'" />
      </div>
      <div class="card-adiest__body">
        <span class="svc-card__badge" style="position:static; margin-bottom:1rem; display:inline-block">🎓 Adiestramiento</span>
        <h3>Programa de adiestramiento</h3>
        <p>Su perro estará hospedado con nosotros <strong>30 días corridos</strong>, donde trabajará diariamente con el adiestrador.</p>

        <h4 style="margin:1.5rem 0 0.75rem; color:var(--green-dark)">Comandos que aprenderá</h4>
        <div class="commands-table">
          <div class="cmd-row header">
            <span>Comando</span>
            <span>Acción</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Junto</span><span>Camina junto al guía, adaptándose a su velocidad y dirección.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Sit</span><span>Se sienta.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Down</span><span>Se echa.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Stá / Parado</span><span>Se para.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Vení</span><span>Acude al llamado siempre.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Quedate</span><span>Se queda en cualquiera de las posiciones aprendidas.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Junto (pasar a)</span><span>Desde cualquier posición asume la posición inicial, sentándose a la izquierda.</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span>Off</span><span>Aprende a no saltar sobre la gente.</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="includes-grid">
          <div class="inc-block">
            <strong>¿Qué incluye?</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>Hospedaje por 30 días</li>
              <li>Traslados incluidos (inicio y fin)</li>
              <li>Alimento premium</li>
              <li>Baños sanitarios</li>
              <li>Asistencia veterinaria permanente</li>
              <li>Informe de avances + instructivo final</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="inc-block guarantee">
            <strong>🛡️ Garantía</strong>
            <p>Garantizamos el correcto funcionamiento de los comandos enseñados <strong>durante 3 meses</strong> después de finalizado el programa.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5491150968576&text=Hola!%20Quiero%20m%C3%A1s%20informaci%C3%B3n%20de%20hospedaje%20para%20mi%20mascota%20en%20Las%20Lunas.%20"
          target="_blank"
          class="btn btn-wa"
          style="margin-top:1.5rem"
        >
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51a12.8 12.8 0 00-.57-.01c-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
          ¡Quiero más información!
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card E: Traslado Internacional -->
    <div class="card-intl reveal" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
      <div class="card-intl__media">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/intl/600/400" alt="Traslado internacional" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="card-intl__body">
        <span class="svc-card__badge" style="position:static; display:inline-block; margin-bottom:1rem">✈️ Internacional</span>
        <div class="latam-logo">
          <a href="https://www.latampettransport.com/es/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <img src="https://www.latampettransport.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Logo-LATAM-PET-TRANSPORT.png" alt="LATAM Pet Transport" loading="lazy" onerror="this.alt='LATAM Pet Transport'" style="height:40px; object-fit:contain;" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <h3>Traslado internacional de mascotas</h3>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.latampettransport.com/es/quote/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="intl-link">
            ¿Viajás con tu mascota? Escribinos por acá y te acompañamos paso a paso para organizar su traslado internacional de forma segura.
          </a>
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.latampettransport.com/es/quote/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:1rem">
          Solicitar cotización →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card F: Generales -->
    <div class="card-generales reveal" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
      <h3 class="card-generales__title">Incluido en todos nuestros servicios</h3>
      <div class="generales-grid reveal-group">
        <div class="gen-item">
          <span class="gen-icon">👁️</span>
          <span>Supervisión permanente</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gen-item">
          <span class="gen-icon">🧹</span>
          <span>Limpieza constante</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gen-item">
          <span class="gen-icon">🛁</span>
          <span>Baños sanitarios</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gen-item">
          <span class="gen-icon">🩺</span>
          <span>Asistencia veterinaria ante urgencias</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gen-item">
          <span class="gen-icon">🍗</span>
          <span>Alimento premium</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Instagram CTA -->
    <div class="ig-cta reveal" style="margin-top:3rem">
      <div class="ig-cta__text">
        <h3>¡Unite a la familia Las Lunas!</h3>
        <p>Vas a encontrar tips prácticos de adiestramiento, conducta y salud para tu mascota</p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/hospedaje.laslunas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary ig-cta__btn">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/></svg>
        ¡Seguinos en Instagram! @hospedaje.laslunas
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.servicios { background: var(--white); }
.servicios__header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

/* Main cards */
.cards-main {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.25rem;
}

.svc-card {
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.1);
  background: var(--white);
  transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
}
.svc-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(45,106,79,0.12);
}

.svc-card__img {
  position: relative;
  height: 220px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--gray-light);
}
.svc-card__img img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; transition:transform 0.4s; }
.svc-card:hover .svc-card__img img { transform: scale(1.06); }

.svc-card__badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1rem;
  left: 1rem;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
  color: var(--green-dark);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
  border-radius: 50px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
}

.svc-card__body { padding: 1.5rem; }
.svc-card__body h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--green-dark); }
.svc-card__body p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--gray-mid); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

.hours {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--green);
  background: var(--green-pale);
  padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Adiestramiento card */
.card-adiest {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 0;
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.1);
  background: var(--white);
}
@media (min-width: 900px) {
  .card-adiest { grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr; }
}

.card-adiest__media { min-height: 300px; background: var(--gray-light); }
.card-adiest__media img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
.card-adiest__body { padding: 2rem 2.5rem; }
.card-adiest__body h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.card-adiest__body > p { color: var(--gray-mid); }

/* Commands table */
.commands-table {
  border: 1px solid var(--green-pale);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
}
.cmd-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--green-pale);
}
.cmd-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.cmd-row span { padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; }
.cmd-row span:first-child {
  background: var(--green-pale);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--green-dark);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--green-pale);
}
.cmd-row span:last-child { color: var(--gray-dark); }
.cmd-row.header span {
  background: var(--green);
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}

/* Includes */
.includes-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) { .includes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

.inc-block { padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--gray-light); border-radius: var(--radius); }
.inc-block strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--green-dark); }
.inc-block ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
.inc-block ul li::before { content: '✓ '; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }
.inc-block ul li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--gray-dark); }

.guarantee { background: var(--green-pale); border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.2); }
.guarantee strong { color: var(--green-dark); }
.guarantee p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--green-dark); line-height: 1.6; }

/* International card */
.card-intl {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.1);
  background: var(--white);
}
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .card-intl { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; }
}
.card-intl__media img { width:100%; height:260px; object-fit:cover; }
.card-intl__body { padding: 2rem; }
.card-intl__body h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.latam-logo { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.intl-link { color: var(--gray-mid); font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--green); text-underline-offset: 3px; }
.intl-link:hover { color: var(--green); }

/* Generales card */
.card-generales {
  background: var(--green-dark);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 2.5rem;
}
.card-generales__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--white);
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.generales-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.gen-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  border-radius: 50px;
  padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.gen-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
.gen-icon { font-size: 1.25rem; }

/* IG CTA */
.ig-cta {
  background: var(--green-pale);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 2.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.15);
}
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .ig-cta { flex-direction: row; text-align: left; }
  .ig-cta__text { flex: 1; }
}
.ig-cta h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; color: var(--green-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.ig-cta p { color: var(--gray-mid); font-size: 0.95rem; }

.svc-card__cta { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
</style>
